You can *hack* your way around. See the following example:

    Stream&lt;List&lt;String&gt;&gt; stream = Stream.of(&quot;Cat&quot;, &quot;Dog&quot;, &quot;Whale&quot;, &quot;Mouse&quot;)
       .collect(Collectors.collectingAndThen(
           Collectors.partitioningBy(a -&gt; a.length() &gt; 3),
